To      Kurusa~
Subject soccer!~
Text
Ok. soccer is ran in a 5x5 arena. On each side is a goal 
(the three center slots on each side) The objective is to 
drag the ball to the opponents goal and kill the ball in
the opponents goal (the ball has INSANE hp).

There is 1 DEFINED goalie at the beginning chosen by the
teams. That person can kill anyone, anywhere....and request
a restore at any time. If anyone else kills someone of the 
other team at a square NOT in goal....they get a yellow
card (trans to satan and then to recall...aloud back in game)
if that yellow carded person does this again in that round, 
they get red carded - out for the round.

Just so you know, mud school arena is where it was held in
the past, PERFECT area. Already 5x5 and easy access from 
recall, so less trouble by you. Teams range from 3-6 (or
more if your daring) per team. Leader appointed at beginning
to chose quested person - back and forth....so teams are even.

-Koas- `^"Always helping"``
~
