Nomyuki tells you 'You do realize you're not allowed to mess with the rottweiler in such a way, right?'
You reply to Nomyuki 'he's summoned in by questors'
Nomyuki replies 'You're speaking to an immortal, and I'd love to hear your excuse on that.  It was declared a long time ago no one was to move the rottweiler from the quest room.'
You reply to Nomyuki 'and how is one supposed to read this rule?'
Nomyuki replies 'Ignorance is not an excuse, I should remind you Mareth.'
You reply to Nomyuki 'just who is this?'
Nomyuki replies 'Kurusa, an Imm. =p'
Nomyuki replies 'Now then, what pker doesn't know about not using Kendo officers or moving the rottweiler?  They're blatant ways to cheat someone into a fight or into death and are both illegal.'
You reply to Nomyuki 'hmmm, I thought both were legal'
Nomyuki replies 'Personally I don't give a hell if you killed me, this is a 1.4k vamp mage and as I'm sure you can tell in the pkfight, I was completely lagged and didn't do anything about it. =P'
Nomyuki replies 'But your manipulation of the rottweiler does bug me.'
You reply to Nomyuki 'I've summoned all the sec nine gate mobs to serenity before.. is that illegal?'
Nomyuki replies 'Only if its a sure death.  Which only includes Tetsuo and Satan, though you CAN fear someone into Satan if you like, and if they're dumb enough for it.'
Nomyuki replies 'But moving the rottweiler is also illegal, since its the default gate location for all questing.'
You reply to Nomyuki 'yeah, but it's not supposed to be'
You reply to Nomyuki 'it's summoned in after a reboot'

blah blah blah

