Sender  Entropy~
Date    Tue Sep 17 21:56:53 2002~
Stamp   1032317813
To      all~
Subject All this PK/RP BS.~
Text
Here's a nice idea. First, lets take RP points, and remove them entirely. Then, let's take the pk
bonuses to autoquesting, and give them to everyone. Before you all jump on me, listen to the logic behind this.
Basically, the way I see it, PKing, like RPing, is something you do because you ENJOY doing it. Why
are we bribing people to do something they should enjoy, and in an ineffective way, I might add.
Without any incentive, I'd still PK, though I'd never RP, but then again, with incentive, I still won't RP.
People are often setting pk to get rich of autoquesting, or to quest out, then remake. People are RPing
just to hero. If you really like doing either one, you'll do it without being bribed.
The reason I suggested making the pk AQ bonus apply to everyone instead of simply removing it is because
as things stand, Kyrn's changes for the most part drastically reduced the effectiveness of aq while
drastically increasing the cost. It was calculated that, working at minimum wage for the amount
of time it takes to get a sash, you could hire several very expensive prostitutes.
And it'd be nice to have the stuff all useable at level 0. I'm being equal opportunity here, I'm not
suggesting this to just hose pkers, or just hose RPers. If you really want, nerf the bonus completely,
I just think it'd be a nice thing for everyone to have it.

If you're pking, do it for the thrill of the chase, do it for that burst of adrenaline, where your heart
starts beating at three times it's normal speed before a fight. Do it for the feeling you get when
you know you've created a monster beast. Or when you're playing a gimp, and you're gonna try and beat a
monster anyways, by guile or otherwise. I've been on both ends, it works both ways. Don't do it because
you can get something special out of it. As for RP, I don't understand, but obviously some people enjoy it
and hey, whatever floats your boat. If you love it, you'll do it, points or no.

--`!E`1n`8t`&r`8o`1p`!y`b, can you see there's a little spot of light in me, can you see, can you see what you wanna see....
~
