Stamp   1033679626
To      all~
Subject Tools~
Text
Tools
------
Tools are special items that will allow you to tune up a weapon or 
armor up to four times. This is done by swapping stats from one weapon 
to another and destroying the weapon the stats were taken from.

What Tools CAN do:
1: They can swap hp, mana, move to a new weapon/armor
2: They can swap hit and dam to a new weapon/armor
3: They can swap a flag to a weapon/armor (Max of 3 on a weapon)

What tools CANNOT (currently) do:
1: Swap damn_nouns
2: Remove weapon flags

----------
Tools do have a limit of what they can do. Powerful eq can be made, but 
only to a certain point within reason. Plus.. keep in mind that eq can 
only be modded up to four times, so choose wisely.

Hit: Maximum of 10 on a weapon or armor. If the weapon or armor already 
has 10 hit, then this cannot add it further.

Dam: Maximum of 10 on a weapon or armor. If the weapon or armor already 
has 10 dam, then this cannot add it further.

Hp: Max of 100. Not to exceed 100 on a armor and 50 on weapon
Mana: Max of 100. Not to exceed 100 on a armor and 50 on weapon
Move: Max of 100. Not to exceed 100 on a armor and 50 on weapon
Move (extra): Special rule here. I will allow 500 move to be transferred to an
armor only ONCE for the price of two tools. But this will also use up 
two modding chances and you can't transfer move of that amount again.
Also, your name will be put onto the eq so that I know who's done it so far.

Ask me `&nicely`` about any explanations about these rules and I'll clarify 
if need be. Some of these rules are subject to change.. any changes will be posted.


P.S: Forgot to mention that Tools cannot mod Aqeq or Qeq. But it can mod stock
or token enhanced items.
~
